    "dom_section_identifier": "cdc-niosh-health-hazard-evaluation-2026-section-0002",
    "position": 1,
    "paragraph_or_text_span": "The NIOSH Health Hazard Evaluation (HHE) program is a free service that evaluates U.S. workplaces for health hazards. Employees, employers, and union officials can request an HHE if they suspect workplace exposures or conditions are harming employees' health. HHEs recommend ways to reduce health hazards and prevent work-related illness and injury.",
